Package org.obrel.space

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ObjectSpace<T>
    An interface that defines hierarchical spaces of relatable objects which can be accessed with URLs.
    ObjectSpaceResolver
    A binary function extension that resolves URLs in object spaces.
    ObjectSpaceResolver.DeleteResolver
    An object space resolver implementation that invokes ObjectSpace.delete(String).
    ObjectSpaceResolver.GetResolver
    An object space resolver implementation that invokes ObjectSpace.get(String).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileSystemSpace<T>
    An object space implementation that maps URLs to the local file system.
    HtmlSpace
    An object space implementation that converts values from another object space into HTML.
    MappedSpace<I,O>
    An ObjectSpace implementation that maps values from another object space.
    ObjectSpaceResolver.PutResolver<T>
    An object space resolver implementation that invokes ObjectSpace.delete(String).
    RelationSpace<T>
    An ObjectSpace implementation that is based on RelatedObject.
    SynchronizedObjectSpace<O>
    A wrapper for other object spaces that synchronizes concurrent access to the object space methods.
